ape as he won his semi-final from gun to tape to move into the Olympic 800 metres final, where he will hope to make it five in a row for Kenya.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Wanyonyi\", \"score\": 0.9999947311428166, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Wanyonyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Wanyonyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Wanyonyi\"}, {\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999988534375213, \"rank\": 1.0985874893809605e-06, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"KHELIF FIGHTS FOR GOLD  Algerian boxer Imane Khelif, who was thrust into the centre of a gender dispute early on at the Paris Games, fights for gold in the women's welterweight category.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1395, \"end\": 1403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9992882946839553, \"rank\": 0.0006894258580283132, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 1410, \"end\": 1422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bout is scheduled for 2051 GMT.\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SOCCER FINAL  Thierry Henry's France side are aiming to win their first Olympic title for 40 years in the men's final while Spain will try to improve on their silver medal in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thierry Henry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\"}, {\"begin\": 1625, \"end\": 1631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9385174827991816, \"rank\": 0.06550963448504721, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1719, \"end\": 1724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8819538768884704, \"rank\": 0.13383395110569463, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1770, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9742120826988354, \"rank\": 0.026470537286824903, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The match is set to kick off at 1600 GMT at Paris' Parc des Princes.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.5806328524099735e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1828, \"end\": 1844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parc_des_Princes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Parc des Princes\